        <h2>
            易经的智慧的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 5 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1987042">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1987042/" class="title-link">易经的智慧</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1987042"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4040883/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4040883-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4040883/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">ZHIYU</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-04-24"
      class="main-meta">2009-04-24 04:42:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1987042_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  “易”“经”可以说是中国古老的哲学体系，它渗透进了我们中华民族的整个古老文化中。从《黄帝内经》到“五行术数”，“四柱”，“紫斗”等等，都以易为理论。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1987042/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
