  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3544716">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3544716/" class="title-link">易经是一部决策论</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3544716"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/39766208/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u39766208-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/39766208/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">和尚</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-14"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-14 12:39:59</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3544716_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  可以说易经是一部决策论，而且是一部全中国人民都在用的决策论。有一句话好像叫做百姓日用而不知的说的就是易。它是中国人思维方式的最高起源与抽象。但在历史的发展中，它并没有被所有人很好的学习，太多一知半解的人对它的运用转变成为了单纯的占。惜哉。。。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
