  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3396721/" class="title-link">占，不占，这是个问题</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3396721"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/37227376/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u37227376-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/37227376/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">anamaria</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-07-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-07-05 00:22:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3396721_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  怀着一种心情前往，却将另一种心情带离.. 我不知道是否总有这种事件... 荀子一句话，彷佛点醒了很多：善易者不占.. 确实，《易经》讲的是世间万物.. 卦象的使然，涵盖万物，绝非占卜如此肤浅... 天行有常，不为尧存，不为桀亡，或许，真谛总是如此显隐.. 放在眼前，却需要自己...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3396721/#comments">(2回应)</a>
